{"tid":2410810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尼日利亞前女財長被選為世貿總幹事","createTime":"2021-02-17T02:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T02:50:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9e448bfd50751e4355e31e964284d6c05982f492","tid":2410810,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575980-20210217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575980-20210217.htm&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=7dab83e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575980-20210217.htm&h=155c422f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575980-20210217.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n世界貿易組織任命尼日利亞前財長奧孔喬-伊韋阿拉出任新總幹事，令她成為首位執掌這個組織的女性總幹事和首位非洲裔總幹事。<br />\n<br />\n中國和美國都期望奧孔喬-伊韋阿拉推動世貿改革。奧孔喬-伊韋阿拉說，上任後會與世貿成員合作，迅速解決疫情大流行帶來的經濟衝擊，又承認世貿需要深層和廣泛改革。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，雖然美國拜登政府一改特朗普前政府的立場，支持奧孔喬-伊韋阿拉出任總幹事，但新政府仍然可能透過阻礙世貿上訴機構法官任命，令世貿的爭端解決機制陷入停擺。"},{"pid":"41f175f888fd64b408363982079a109223ee3d8b","tid":2410810,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞貿易好發達架咩？<br />\n<br />\n佢自己都未搞得掂自己個國家<br />\n<br />\n搵佢做世界貿易？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會好笑咗D？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8241088a805092022e54f6055f1a75fe6e600f","tid":2410810,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"一大堆垃圾國家串通買中共投票選一個女板談得菜出嚟"},{"pid":"8f7ae8ab23bf76a8606c5c4f5376650a6b63c56d","tid":2410810,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:16:01.000Z","msg":"fucking nigger"},{"pid":"595ce2dba939f2a934a3ce6cc8f9344435040981","tid":2410810,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5b8241088